PRIVACY POLICY
mightyIT Apps do collects user information from you so that we can provide a rich and better user experience. We are very concerned about your Privacy. And this Privacy policy explains how we use, protect user information.
Any of the information we collect from you may be used to personalize your experience
(your information helps us to better respond to your individual needs)
Information  about how we use the user data
-
User Location
: mightyIT app may take user location with user consent for some apps to work properly and give the required services.
-
Camera  Permission
: App will access your camera only after you give us your consent.
-
Phone Number/SIM Details
: With your consent, we collect your phone number and SIM information to ensure that requests made through the app originate from authorized devices. This helps in maintaining the integrity and security of our services.
The information that we collect will be used to contact or identify you only when necessary. We do not share this information with external parties except as described in this policy
How we protect your information
We implement a variety of security measures to maintain the safety of your personal information, including your phone number and other details.
Information we get from your use of our services
We may collect information about the services that you use and how you use them, such as when you view and interact with our content. We may collect device-specific information (such as your hardware model, operating system version, unique device identifiers, and mobile network information). App will not share that information with third parties.
