User Consent
We obtain your consent before collecting any personal data. Consent is explicitly obtained through a disclosure and consent screen within the app that details the data collected and its usage. You have the right to withdraw your consent at any time.
User Rights
You have the right to access, correct, and delete your personal data. For requests, please email us at
it@memighty.com
. We will respond to your request within a reasonable timeframe.
Privacy Questions
If you have any questions or concerns about our Privacy Policy or data processing, please email us at
it@memighty.com
.
We may update Privacy Policy from time to time. When we change the 
policy in a material way, a notice will be posted on our website along 
with the updated Privacy Policy.